n 48 hours."}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"Resolution"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We will invite you to a meeting or arrange a phone call to discuss and hopefully resolve your complaint. We will do this within 14 days of sending you the acknowledgement letter."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Within three days of the meeting, we will write to you to confirm what took place and any solutions we have agreed with you."}]]}]]}]}]}]]}]
